For base frosting: Using electric mixer, beat butter in large bowl until fluffy. Gradually beat in sugar, then cream and vanilla. Divide between 2 bowls.
For vanilla frosting: Mix 1 teaspoon vanilla into 1 bowl of base frosting.
For almond frosting: Mix almond extract into second bowl of base frosting. Mix in yellow food coloring, 1 drop at a time, until desired shade is reached.
